df <- fromJSON("/Users/abby/Desktop/DataJournalism/R4CSS-master/data/.json")

df <- df %>%
  rename(
    Age = Category1Title,
    City = Category2Title,
    Gender = Category3Title,

    Count = Val
  )%>%
  mutate(Year = YearRaw / 100) %>%
  select(-Category4Title, -Category5Title) %>%
  mutate(
    City = ifelse(City == "", "", City)

gender_ratio_df <- df %>%
  filter(Age == "", Year %in% c(102, 112)) %>%
  group_by(City, Year, Gender) %>%
  summarise(Count = sum(Count), .groups = "drop") %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = Gender, values_from = Count) %>%
  mutate(Ratio =  / )

# 
map_df <- map_data %>%
  left_join(gender_ratio_df, by = c("COUNTYNAME" = "City")) %>%
  mutate(
    centroid = st_centroid(geometry),
    coord_x = st_coordinates(centroid)[, 1],
    coord_y = st_coordinates(centroid)[, 2],
    label_x = ifelse(COUNTYNAME == "", coord_x + 0.15, coord_x),
    label_y = ifelse(COUNTYNAME == "", coord_y - 0.1, coord_y)
  )

# 
library(shadowtext)
ggplot(map_df) +
  geom_sf(aes(fill = Ratio), color = "white") +
  geom_shadowtext(
    aes(x = label_x, y = label_y, label = round(Ratio, 1),size=1),
    color = "white", bg.color = "black",
    size = 2.5, fontface = "bold"
  ) +
  scale_fill_gradient(low = "red", high = "lightgrey") +
  facet_wrap(~Year) +
  coord_sf(xlim = c(119.5, 122.2), ylim = c(21.7, 25.5), expand = FALSE) +
  theme_void() +

age_trend_df <- df %>%
  filter(Gender == "",Age != "", Year %in% 97:112) %>%
  filter(Age != "")%>%
  group_by(Year, Age) %>%
  summarise(Total = sum(Count), .groups = "drop") %>%
  mutate(AgeGroup = ordered(Age, 
    levels=c("0-6", "6-12",
    "12-18","18-24", "24-30",
    "30-40", "40-50", "50-65",
    "65",""),
    label = c("0-11", "0-11",
    "(12-23)","(12-23)", 
    "(24-39)","(24-39)",
    "(40-64)", "(40-64)",
    "(65)",""))) %>%
  group_by(Year, AgeGroup) %>%
  summarise(Total = sum(Total), .groups = "drop")

# 
ggplot(age_trend_df, aes(x = Year, y = Total, color = AgeGroup)) +
